# Sky culture name
msgid "Sardinian"
msgstr "Sarde"

# Sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"Like all peoples of the world, even the ancient Sardinians, turned their "
"eyes to the sky that marked the time and the seasons. The peasant's world "
"has given its name to the stars and the constellations of the Sardinian "
"culture."
msgstr ""
"Comme tous les peuples du monde, même les anciens Sardes, tournaient leurs "
"yeux vers le ciel qui marquait le temps et les saisons. Le monde paysan a "
"donné son nom aux étoiles et aux constellations de la culture sarde."

